    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and is ready for its next owner. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, reflecting a consistent maintenance schedule. The exterior retains a strong shine with only minor surface blemishes typical of careful use, and the interior is clean and comfortable with no major wear or tear. This is a reliable, high-quality car that offers a great balance of performance and value for someone looking for a dependable daily driver.",
