    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of her, and honestly, she still looks and drives like she just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s rare to find one in such pristine, showroom-level condition. If you're looking for your dream ride that\u2019s been loved and pampered, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
