    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, a masterclass in longitudinal FR packaging. This example features the revered F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC power plant, delivering a high-revving, naturally aspirated experience paired with a precise, close-ratio six-speed manual gearbox. The structural integrity of the X-bone monocoque frame is absolute, providing a rigid platform for the factory-tuned double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential. Every component is original, from the heat-shielding on the manifold to the factory-spec bushings, ensuring the tactile feedback and mechanical harmony intended by Shigeru Uehara. This is a pristine, unmodified specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
