    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2020 Porsche 718 Cayman S, preserved in a state that rivals its original delivery day. This vehicle has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the leather upholstery remains supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Every service milestone has been documented and performed exclusively by certified technicians, with a comprehensive binder of maintenance records included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, this car is mechanically and aesthetically perfect. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a modern masterpiece that has been pampered since day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
